#read in data

ogsurveyresponses <- read.csv(file='../data/SL_followup/survey_responsesOGrun.csv') #score PAS, BMRQ, and goldMSI

followup <- read.csv(file='../data/SL_followup/Groove)_March 22, 2023_07.53.csv') #score everything

#MET cleaning/scoring

#double check this is accurate
MET_cleaned <- MET %>%
  dplyr::select(Participant.Public.ID, Response, Correct, display) %>%
  subset(Response != "AUDIO PLAY REQUESTED") %>%
  subset(Response != "") %>%
  subset(display !="Practice") %>%
  subset(display !="practice_ritmo")

melodic_score <- MET_cleaned %>%
  subset(display == "Melodia") %>%
  group_by(Participant.Public.ID) %>%
  summarise_at(vars(Correct), list(name = sum))

names(melodic_score)[2] <- "MET_melodicscore"

rhythmic_score <- MET_cleaned %>%
  subset(display == "Ritmo") %>%
  group_by(Participant.Public.ID) %>%
  summarise_at(vars(Correct), list(name = sum))
names(rhythmic_score)[2] <- "MET_rhythmicscore"

MET_scores <- merge(melodic_score, rhythmic_score)
